  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Build Container Schools For African Children</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">There are countless creches (kindergartens) in disadvantaged areas in Port Elizabeth that arent government funded &amp; poverty stricken. Parents of children do not pay school fees. The classrooms are made of tin shacks, commonly overcrowded, cold in winter and hot in summer, with little ventilation nor space to move. We are dedicated to changing this. We buy/remodel shipping containers to create better learning environments. We also revamp the entire creche turning it into a fully fledged school.</narrative>
  </description>
